                              [sic]: <locus target="#12r">fol. 12r</locus> ዘሐምሌ: <locus target="#14r">fol. 14r</locus> ዘነሐሴ: <locus target="#16v">fol.
                                 16v</locus> ዘመስከረም: <locus target="#18r">fol. 18r</locus> ዘጥቅምት:
                                 <locus target="#20r">fol. 20r</locus> ዘኅዳር: <locus target="#22r">fol. 22r</locus> ዘታህሳስ: <locus target="#23v">fol. 23v</locus> ዘጥር:
                                 <locus target="#25r">fol. 25r</locus> ዘየካቲት: <locus target="#27r">fol. 27r</locus> ዘግንቦት: <locus target="#35v">fol. 35v</locus> ዘሰኔ:
